Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: SOF: Intel: remove mutual exclusion between NOCODEC and HDA_LINK
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: fdecd4aaf80af23f946ad97f6fb90c1f553fcdcc
